44. Disposal of a subsidiary

Disposal of a subsidiary in 2017

On 2 November 2017, a 59.6% owned subsidiary, Acibadem Poliklinikleri AS. (“POL) disposed of its 60% equity interest in SESU Ozel Saglik Hizmetleri Tibbi Malzemeler ve Ticaret AS. (“SESU”) to Ali Suat Gulluoglu (“Disposal) which was satisfied by share swap with Ali Suat Gulluoglu for his 30.10% equity interest in Medlife Clinic Ambulance ve Ozel Saglik Hizmetleri Ithalat ve lhracat AS. (“Medlife”). Following the Disposal, SESU ceased to be a subsidiary of POL)
